OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThe day will start with low
OL,6,Fcloud, mist and fog patches around,
OL,7,Fthough these should lift readily
OL,8,Fduring the morning to leave sunny
OL,9,Fspells. A small chance of a light
OL,10,Fshower near North Sea coasts. Feeling
OL,11,Fwarm in gentle winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FAn isolated light shower is
OL,14,Fstill possible overnight, chiefly near
OL,15,Fto the east coast. For most though it
OL,16,Fwill stay dry with clear spells.
OL,17,FPatchy low cloud and fog forming.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
