OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FLow cloud or fog will clear
OL,6,Fto leave plenty of fine weather with
OL,7,Fsunny spells on Thursday. However,
OL,8,Fcloud could bubble up sufficiently in
OL,9,Fplaces to produce a light shower.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FThe
OL,12,Fweather should remain fine on Friday
OL,13,Fwith further spells of warm sunshine.
OL,14,FHowever, the weekend looks slightly
OL,15,Fcooler and more breezy with the chance
OL,16,Fof some rain at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
